com.hazelcast.internal.adapter

Interface DataStructureAdapter<K,V>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ICacheDataStructureAdapter, IMapDataStructureAdapter, ReplicatedMapDataStructureAdapter, TransactionalMapDataStructureAdapter

    public interface DataStructureAdapter<K,V>
    Abstracts the Hazelcast data structures with Near Cache support for the Near Cache usage.
